sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Col, Container, Image, ListGroup, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'; import cardImage from './../../assets/images/cardImage.png'; import './Card.css'; const Card = ({ ...props }) => { const { Name, Birthday, Phone, Email, InsuranceInfo } = props.data; console.log(Name); return ( {Name} {Birthday} {Phone} {Email} {InsuranceInfo} ); }; export default Card;
